---
import SEO from '../../components/SEO.astro';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="bg-[#030303]">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <SEO title="Terms of Service - BandhanNova Sentinel" />
  
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-[#030303] text-gray-300 font-sans min-h-screen relative overflow-x-hidden selection:bg-fuchsia-500/30 selection:text-white">
  <!-- Premium Background Glows -->
  <div class="absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[50vw] h-[50vw] rounded-full bg-fuchsia-600/5 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[50vw] h-[50vw] rounded-full bg-violet-600/5 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <!-- Decorative grid overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.007)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.007)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:40px_40px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <header class="border-b border-white/5 bg-[#030303]/40 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0 z-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 h-20 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
        <img src="/favicon.ico" alt="Sentinel Logo" class="w-9 h-9 object-contain" />
        <span class="text-xl tracking-widest bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-400 to-fuchsia-400 mt-0.5" style="font-family: 'Virgo 01', sans-serif;">
          Sentinel
        </span>
      </a>
      <a href="/signin" class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 hover:text-white uppercase tracking-wider transition-colors" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
        Go to Dashboard →
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24 relative z-10">
    <div class="space-y-4 mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-fuchsia-500/10 border border-fuchsia-500/20 text-fuchsia-400 text-xs font-semibold">
        ⚖️ Terms & Conditions
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-none" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        Last Updated: July 1, 2026 • Version 1.0.0
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-gray-400 font-normal" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
      
      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By creating an account, installing the Sentinel SDK, or using the BandhanNova Sentinel web applications, you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, you must immediately terminate use of our platform.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">2. Account Creation and Google OAuth</h2>
        <p>
          To use Sentinel, you must link your identity using Google Sign-In. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your session token and auth cookies. You agree to notify us immediately of any unauthorized access.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">3. Integration SDK License</h2>
        <p>
          We grant you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, fully-revocable license to integrate the `sentinel-sdk` script into your production applications. You may not modify or reverse-engineer the core communication mechanisms of the SDK with malicious intent.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">4. Data Usage and Telemetry Responsibility</h2>
        <p>
          You are solely responsible for the contents of the logs, stack traces, and environment details transmitted to Sentinel. You must ensure that your applications do not transmit unmasked Personally Identifiable Information (PII) or sensitive health/financial data, in compliance with standard privacy rules.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">5. Limitations and Disclaimers</h2>
        <p>
          BandhanNova Sentinel is provided "as is" and "as available." While we offer high availability via multi-node Turso relays, we do not warrant that log processing or AI heuristics will be uninterrupted, completely accurate, or free from latency.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">6. Termination of Service</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that breach these terms, exceed platform query limits excessively, or engage in activity that degrades service quality for other developers.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-white/5 py-12 text-center text-xs text-gray-600 bg-[#020202]">
    <p>© 2026 BandhanNova Platforms. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
